channel.title: Looking for an Axoloti in EU
channel.description: Hello, I'll have a project with young kids in 2022. I would love to make an electronic instrument with them, and give them. Axoloti would be perfect for what i have in mind. So if someone has one for sale, please let me know ;) thank you ! maxime
